Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.34,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.18,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,But then another girl confessed\N her feelings to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:18.90,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.75,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I started going out with a girl recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:31.26,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I confessed my feelings to Saki-chan, \Nwho I've been close to since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:35.54,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,She accepted, and now we're going steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.90,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:42.04,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm the happiest person on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.69,main,Shino,0,0,0,,Sakisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.66,main,Shino,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.68,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.64,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I'm headed off to my club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:55.53,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.53,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll wait until you're done, Saki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.52,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You can go on ahead for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.75,main,Saki,0,0,0,,But no cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.02,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,S-Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.67,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Did you think I would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.76,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.76,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:26.17,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll love you even more so you'll never \Nhave to worry about me cheating on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.44,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.10,main,Saki,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:29.94,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.94,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I love you, Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.81,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.12,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.09,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Feel my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.14,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:39.84,main,,0,0,0,,You feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.10,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.44,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I get it! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.58,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Save that for when we're alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.79,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Naoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.34,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You're beyond sincere. You're just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.51,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You can't even take a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.10,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,A-Am I that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.18,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You're pretty damn weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.74,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.97,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Like what you did to me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.01,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.44,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.52,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But I want to be true to my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.98,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I can't help but tell someone \NI love them when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.23,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Wh-What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:17.74,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.03,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I confessed to you once a month \Nsince we were in first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.54,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Now, in high school, you finally said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.48,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Of course I'm going to cherish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.51,main,Saki,0,0,0,,That was way too much for \Nelementary and middle school me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.55,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But now you embrace my feelings for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.00,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Oh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.96,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.51,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.84,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:44.97,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.43,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You were as cute as ever today!
