Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.44,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:56.69,italics,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.61,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.25,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:14.49,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You're M-Mukai Naoya-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.59,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Yes, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.04,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.12,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.12,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.94,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I have feelings for you!
