Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.54,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Sorry, I haven't even introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.75,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Wait... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:17.37,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Minase Nagisa. I'm a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.75,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.41,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.68,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.42,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,What do you think of me, looks-wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.64,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Well, if I had to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.39,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're cute as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.47,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.72,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I worked so hard these past \Nfew months for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.86,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.15,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Four hours of working out, \Njogging, and yoga every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.56,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Working on myself for three \Nhours before bed every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.37,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're such a hard worker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.61,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I wanted to be in my best \Ncondition for my confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.12,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,What an upright person you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.46,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,They say the best way to a man's \Nheart is through his stomach, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.04,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I practiced cooking for eight hours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.84,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried about your health?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.30,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You have to take care of your own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.26,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.60,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.80,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.22,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'd like you to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.90,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.92,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't put \Nyourself out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.61,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,No, it was for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.94,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,In fact, I had fun doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:37.45,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Besides, I think a big part of why it \Ntastes good is the Matsusaka beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.74,top,,0,0,0,,Would you like a bag for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.54,main,,0,0,0,,lobster, and foie gras that I bought\N with money from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.06,top,,0,0,0,,What a long day.
