Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.34,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You overdid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.38,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,B-But that's so commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.60,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.47,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Do I seem attractive to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.70,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.81,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,You're attractive as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.38,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Th-Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.65,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.66,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Would you please go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:27.38,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Am I not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.13,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.60,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I bet I'd be super happy \Nif I could go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.43,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.87,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I already have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:53.50,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I guess... I should have expected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:58.83,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to give up just \Nbecause I got turned down once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.25,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll come confess to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.88,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I-I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.68,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,It's true that I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:28.36,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I love her, and I want \Nto treasure her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.06,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Naoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:33.36,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But it's true that I think you're attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:39.37,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So I want you in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.75,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I don't want to turn you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.87,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But I can't betray my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.83,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So if it isn't too outrageous to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.65,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Can I date both of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.23,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Could you come with me to ask my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:56.41,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.24,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'm sorry this is the \Nonly thing I can propose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.85,main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.38,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Let's go give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.30,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.45,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:23.58,sign_13417_149_Club_Meet,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,330)}Club\NMeet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:23.58,sign_5658_74_Girlfriend__Girl,Text,0,0,0,,{\move(880,460,930,490)\frz19.23\bord4\fs70}Girlfriend, Girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.53,main,Shino,0,0,0,,Go, Sakisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.19,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:27.21,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Man, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:31.50,main,Shino,0,0,0,,You killed it again, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.21,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.12,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.60,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.37,main,Shino,0,0,0,,You two sure are attached at the hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.07,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Wha... Shino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.35,main,Shino,0,0,0,,I don't want to get in the way. \NI'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.50,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What's up? What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.79,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,It's about this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.85,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.96,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'm Minase Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.38,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Sh-She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.80,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Who is this girl? Oh my God, she's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.88,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Let's go hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.59,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Okay? Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.88,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But there's something important \Nwe need to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.30,main,Saki,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to talk about anything \Nif we don't even know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.18,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.81,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.83,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.27,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.74,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. I'm not a good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.13,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You're so cute when you're embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.37,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.88,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.70,main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.48,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Your underwear's cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.50,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.98,main,Saki,0,0,0,,This is too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.68,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I want to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.43,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.86,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan, what do you think of Minase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.60,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.08,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Honestly, I want to go out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:13.24,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.41,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.83,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You have me, Naoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.86,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.37,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:33.08,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So I want to date both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.45,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.37,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.34,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:45.72,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,The truth is, Minase-san just \Nconfessed to me earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.43,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,The more I got to know her, \Nthe more attracted I became.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.96,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm infatuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.25,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.19,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.23,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I can't think of a solution besides \Ngoing out with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.32,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,{\fs40}I can't think of a solution besides \Ngoing out with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.24,italics,Naoya,0,0,0,,{\fs32}I can't think of a solution besides \Ngoing out with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.49,italics,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.41,italics,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.24,italics,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.16,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:18.00,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I can't bring myself to date \Nboth of you in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:22.24,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So with your approval,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:26.82,main,,0,0,0,,I would like to date both of you,\Nhonest and out in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.27,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Did you seriously think I'd say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:40.14,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I-I want us to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:41.99,main,Saki,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:46.03,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I really do feel bad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.49,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Then don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.95,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You have me! Isn't that good enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.83,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,It was until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.97,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.40,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.96,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Can we please avoid violence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.22,main,Saki,0,0,0,,But you're okay with cheating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.33,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Actually, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.93,main,Saki,0,0,0,,How are you even okay with \Nhim dating two girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.24,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.96,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I can't imagine Naoya-kun \Nwould ever break up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:18.48,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll only be rejected if I {\i1}don't{\i0} \Nhave him date both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.44,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,So I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.15,main,Saki,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.87,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.11,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What do you even like so much about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.59,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Naoya-kun is everything to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.87,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.62,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Saki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.25,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Please let us both date him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.88,main,Saki,0,0,0,,T-Too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.46,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Please don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.40,main,Saki,0,0,0,,One guy for one girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.09,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Isn't that common sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:51.05,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,But it's true that I'm \Nattracted to Minase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.95,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So rejecting her and continuing \Nto go out with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.23,main,,0,0,0,,in the name of common \Nsense would be dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.25,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Both to myself and to you, Saki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:04.40,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Lying and going out with two girls \Nwould both leave me with regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:08.57,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,So I want to be honest to myself \Nand try going out with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.62,main,Saki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:16.12,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,What might I do to increase the \Nchances that you'll say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.75,main,Saki,0,0,0,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.29,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,There must be a good solution to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.50,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.99,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I won't spare any effort \Nto make it a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.43,main,Saki,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.55,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Can we just try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.75,main,,0,0,0,,Oh, for—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.82,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.34,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll make snacks every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.23,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You'll always have plenty to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.50,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of you, Saki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.42,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll give you 30,000 yen every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.19,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.89,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll do anything in my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.11,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Why are you stripping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.57,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I agree that it's selfish of me \Nto want to date two girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.70,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I wholly expect you to dump \Nme right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.62,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:02.00,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,And I'm sure Minase-san would prefer \Nif it were just me and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:06.43,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Still, Minase-san, Saki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:13.27,main,,0,0,0,,I promise to make sure that, someday, \Nyou'll be glad you both dated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.43,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Naoya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.19,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Oh, hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:29.65,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Why don't you try making me say that,\N if you really think you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.36,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.79,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I don't think you'll ever do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:36.72,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.12,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:41.31,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I already kind of hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.92,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I-I'll do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.31,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I... I should have thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.94,sign_5658_74_Girlfriend__Girl,Saki,0,0,0,,{\frz19.23\bord4\fs70\move(920,480,950,500)}Girlfriend, Girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.94,sign_13417_149_Club_Meet,Saki,0,0,0,,{\bord8\pos(360,410)\fs20\fad(2108,1)}I...\NI should have\N thought this\N through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.68,main,Saki,0,0,0,,So what are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.21,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,For you two to be all right with \Nboth of you being my girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.66,main,,0,0,0,,you'll have to get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.64,main,Saki,0,0,0,,There's nothing good that can come of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.56,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.64,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Let's live together at my \Nplace. The three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.52,main,Saki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.13,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I don't live with my parents. It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.35,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.03,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I-I'd be okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.08,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll bring my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.34,top,,0,0,0,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.96,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,I'll let your mom know, Saki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:16.62,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.29,main,Saki,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.62,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.48,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Are we seriously going to live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.04,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:30.26,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll prepare rooms for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.22,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll prepare dinner, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.76,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,And, um... Saki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:40.01,main,Saki,0,0,0,,I don't mean to brag, but I'm \Nterrible at doing chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.60,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Of course. You can take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.34,main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.56,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.92,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya, I want a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.03,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.45,main,Saki,0,0,0,,It smells so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.34,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.16,main,Saki,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.88,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.67,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,The bath's ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.17,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You're so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.43,main,Saki,0,0,0,,This is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.03,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan, want me to rub your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.89,main,Saki,0,0,0,,You don't need to do that for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.40,italics,Saki,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.98,italics,Saki,0,0,0,,This might not be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.83,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.15,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,P-Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.23,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Is it all right if we bathe together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.91,main,Saki,0,0,0,,N-Nagisa-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.66,main,Saki,0,0,0,,T-Together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.00,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with you.
